attributes.description: The primary color that the tab is activates

attributes.name: inactive-color
attributes.description: The primary color that the tab is not activated

attributes.name: disabled-color
attributes.description: The primary color that the tab is disabled

attributes.name: indicator-color
attributes.description: The tab activates the color of the indicator

attributes.name: indicator-size
attributes.description: Tab activates the size of the indicator

attributes.name: elevation
attributes.description: Elevation level, options `true` `false` and level of `0-24`

attributes.name: sticky-css-mode
attributes.description: Whether to enable sticky layouts native css sticky mode

attributes.name: safe-area
attributes.description: Whether to enable bottom safe area adaptation

attributes.name: scrollable
attributes.description: Whether to enable scrollable, optional value of `auto` `always`

attributes.name: indicator-position
attributes.description: The position of the indicator, optional value of `normal` `reverse`

events.name: click
events.description: Triggered when the tab is clicked, but not when the tab `disabled` status is `true`

events.name: change
events.description: Triggered when switching tab

attributes.name: v-model:active
attributes.description: The identity of the active tab

attributes.name: header-color
attributes.description: Color of picker header. If not specified it will use the color defined by color prop or the default picker color.

attributes.name: elevation
attributes.description: Elevation level, options `true` `false` and level of `0-24`

attributes.name: allowed-time
attributes.description: Restricts which time can be selected

events.name: change
events.description: Emitted after time changed

attributes.name: type
attributes.description: Tooltip type, Can be set to `default` `primary` `info` `success` `warning` `danger`

attributes.name: offset-x
attributes.description: The x-axis offset, relative to the tooltip-aligned position

attributes.name: offset-y
attributes.description: The y-axis offset, relative to the tooltip-aligned position

attributes.name: teleport
attributes.description: The location of the tooltip mount

attributes.name: same-width
attributes.description: Whether to same width as trigger element

attributes.name: trigger
attributes.description: Tooltip trigger method, optional value is `click` `hover`, `click` is triggered when clicked, `hover` is triggered when hovered

attributes.name: reference
attributes.description: The associated trigger element selector is used to specify specific child elements as trigger elements

events.name: open
events.description: Triggered when the `Tooltip` is opened

events.name: opened
events.description: Triggered when the open `Tooltip` animation ends

events.name: close
events.description: Triggered when the `Tooltip` is closed

events.name: closed
events.description: Triggered when the closing `Tooltip` animation ends

attributes.name: accept
attributes.description: Accepted file type, consistent with the native attribute

attributes.name: capture
attributes.description: Get the file, the same as the native property

attributes.name: elevation
attributes.description: Elevation level, options `true` `false` and level of `0-24`, not in simple mode

attributes.name: hide-list
attributes.description: Whether to hide the file list

attributes.name: validate-trigger
attributes.description: Timing to trigger validation， The optional value is `onChange` `onRemove`

attributes.name: rules
attributes.description: The validation rules，Returns `true` to indicate that the validation passed，The remaining values are converted to text as user prompts

events.name: before-read
events.description: Trigger returns a false value before a file is read to prevent the file from being read(support promise)

events.name: after-read
events.description: Triggered after the file is read

events.name: oversize
events.description: Triggered when the file size limit is exceeded

events.name: before-remove
events.description: Triggered before file deletion, return false value to prevent file deletion (support promise)

events.name: remove
events.description: Triggered when deleting a file. There is a true value to prevent deleting a file (support promise)
